    {
      "id": "ts_sprint_general_1",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_sprint_planning_w12",
      "speaker_id": "spk_jamie",
      "start_time_seconds": 60,
      "end_time_seconds": 90,
      "text": "From last sprint, the analytics dashboard shipped on time, but the notifications revamp slipped by two days.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-03-02T18:31:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-02T18:31:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ts_sprint_action_alex",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_sprint_planning_w12",
      "speaker_id": "spk_alex",
      "start_time_seconds": 300,
      "end_time_seconds": 315,
      "text": "I will update the sprint board and reassign the unclaimed tickets right after this call.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-03-02T18:40:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-02T18:40:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ts_sprint_action_jamie",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_sprint_planning_w12",
      "speaker_id": "spk_jamie",
      "start_time_seconds": 330,
      "end_time_seconds": 345,
      "text": "I will coordinate with the design team to confirm the assets we need for the new onboarding flow.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-03-02T18:41:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-02T18:41:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ts_sprint_action_taylor",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_sprint_planning_w12",
      "speaker_id": "spk_taylor",
      "start_time_seconds": 360,
      "end_time_seconds": 375,
      "text": "I will prepare a rollout checklist for the Q4 roadmap items by Friday.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-03-02T18:42:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-02T18:45:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ts_sprint_general_2",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_sprint_planning_w12",
      "speaker_id": "spk_taylor",
      "start_time_seconds": 200,
      "end_time_seconds": 220,
      "text": "Capacity-wise, we can take on two large stories and three small bug fixes this sprint.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-03-02T18:33:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-02T18:33:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ts_client_intro",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_client_kickoff_01",
      "speaker_id": "spk_account_exec",
      "start_time_seconds": 10,
      "end_time_seconds": 40,
      "text": "Thanks everyone for joining the client kickoff. Today we’ll walk through goals, timelines, and how we’ll use these transcripts.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-03-01T16:00:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-01T16:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ts_client_requirements",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_client_kickoff_01",
      "speaker_id": "spk_client_pm",
      "start_time_seconds": 120,
      "end_time_seconds": 150,
      "text": "Our main requirements are accurate speaker labels, easy sharing with stakeholders, and secure access controls.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-03-01T16:05:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-01T16:05:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ts_client_next_steps",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_client_kickoff_01",
      "speaker_id": "spk_account_exec",
      "start_time_seconds": 900,
      "end_time_seconds": 930,
      "text": "We will share the finalized implementation timeline and invite you to the next milestone review by early next week.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-03-01T16:15:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-01T16:15:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ts_q4_roadmap_overview",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_q4_roadmap_01",
      "speaker_id": "spk_alex",
      "start_time_seconds": 30,
      "end_time_seconds": 60,
      "text": "For the Q4 roadmap, we’re focusing on reliability, collaboration features, and deeper analytics for meeting performance.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-02-20T17:00:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-02-20T17:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ts_q4_roadmap_timeline",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_q4_roadmap_01",
      "speaker_id": "spk_engineer_1",
      "start_time_seconds": 300,
      "end_time_seconds": 330,
      "text": "The collaboration updates should be ready for beta by mid-November, with GA planned for early December.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-02-20T17:10:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-02-20T17:10:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ts_q4_roadmap_risks",
      "transcript_id": "transcript_q4_roadmap_01",
      "speaker_id": "spk_jamie",
      "start_time_seconds": 540,
      "end_time_seconds": 560,
      "text": "The main risks are integration delays with the calendar providers and potential scope creep on live collaboration.",
      "merged_from_segment_ids": [],
      "created_at": "2026-02-20T17:15:00Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-02-20T17:15:00Z"
    },
